Key responsibilities of the role include:
- Perform risk assessment to cover process and security issues from technology perspective
- Conduct security assessments for IT systems and applications & Network components, knowledge about application security assessment will be an advantage
- Review and draft security standards and processes as per industry best practices - Review Architecture from Security aspect - Support and provide expertise for ISO/COBIT framework
- Evaluate new products/technologies from security aspect
The successful candidate will possess a minimum of 4 years technical experience in this space. Job seekers with a Penetration testing background will be desirable. Candidates based outside the GCC will also be considered. A competitive tax free package will be on offer.
